&lt;root&gt;&lt;empty_tag/&gt;&lt;foo&gt;Ņ&lt;/foo&gt;&lt;/root&gt;
~~~

You can see no more `&amp;#x145;` entity but instead just `Ņ` in Unicode (UTF-8 encoded). The [XML declaration](https://xmlwriter.net/xml_guide/xml_declaration.shtml) also shows now the encoding.

